sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant UI as Chat UI (Browser)
    participant API as /api/chat (Next.js Proxy)
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant AI as Gemini + MCPs

    Note over UI: Estado: empty state<br/>Sprite: idle_half_blink

    U->>UI: Escribe pregunta (≤1000 chars)
    UI->>UI: isTokenExpired? → válido
    UI->>UI: Agrega msg user (amber bubble)
    UI->>UI: setLoading(true)

    Note over UI: Sprite header: thinking_squint

    UI->>API: POST /api/chat {message}

    Note over API: Proxy checks (no rate limit aquí)
    API->>API: 1. getServerSession() → id_token
    API->>API: 2. Validate body.message (tipo + largo)
    API->>API: 3. Prompt injection filter (16 regex)
    API->>API: 4. Inyecta X-API-Key server-side

    alt Prompt injection detectada
        API-->>UI: 200 {reply: "Solo respondo info electoral"}
        Note over API: 0 tokens gastados, gateway no enterado
    else Request limpio
        API->>GW: POST /api/chat<br/>Authorization: Bearer id_token<br/>X-API-Key: gk_web_...<br/>X-Real-IP: client_ip

        Note over GW: Gateway aplica rate limiting
        alt Rate limit excedido (Redis)
            GW-->>API: 429 Retry-After: 3600
            API-->>UI: 429
            UI->>UI: "Alcanzaste el límite de consultas"
        else Token budget excedido
            GW-->>API: 429 Daily budget exceeded
            API-->>UI: 429
        else OK
            GW->>AI: Agent con Gemini + MCP tools
            AI-->>GW: reply + sources + warnings
            GW-->>API: {reply, sources, warnings, session_id}
            API-->>UI: JSON response
        end
    end

    UI->>UI: Agrega msg assistant (dark card)
    UI->>UI: setLoading(false)

    Note over UI: Sprite: explaining_talking<br/>Sources chips + warnings ámbar

    alt Error de red / timeout
        UI->>UI: Sprite: loading_worried
        UI->>UI: Mensaje de error amigable
    end
